OL,3,CHarry: I needed to deal with 'stuff
OL,4,Cfrom the past' before having children
OL,6,FThe Duke of Sussex said he knew he
OL,7,F"had stuff from the past that I needed
OL,8,Fto deal with" before having children,
OL,9,Fas he discussed his experience of
OL,10,Ftherapy in Melbourne.
OL,12,FHarry made the comments while giving a
OL,13,Ftalk on stage at an event about
OL,14,Ffatherhood hosted by Movember on
OL,15,FWednesday morning during his visit to
OL,16,FAustralia.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
