CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776243304
OL,3,CHarry: I needed to deal with 'stuff
OL,4,Cfrom the past' before having children
OL,6,FThe duke met with supporters of the
OL,7,Fmen's health charity at the Whitten
OL,8,FOval, which is the training and
OL,9,Fadministrative headquarters of
OL,10,FAustralian rules football club Western
OL,11,FBulldogs.
OL,13,FHarry was presented with personalised
OL,14,FWestern Bulldogs miniature shirts with
OL,15,FArchie and Lilibet's names printed on
OL,16,Fthe back after arriving at the stadium.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776243304
OL,3,CHarry: I needed to deal with 'stuff
OL,4,Cfrom the past' before having children
OL,6,FWhile discussing his experience of
OL,7,Ftherapy before his children were born,
OL,8,FHarry said: "Certainly from a therapy
OL,9,Fstandpoint, you want to be the best
OL,10,Fversion of yourself for your kids.
OL,12,F"And I knew that I had stuff from the
OL,13,Fpast that I needed to deal with, and
OL,14,Ftherefore prepare myself to basically
OL,15,Fcleanse myself of the past."
OL,26,@pD@MOUtD@AOUwD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776243304
OL,3,CHarry: I needed to deal with 'stuff
OL,4,Cfrom the past' before having children
OL,6,FIn a discussion on stage with
OL,7,FMovember's global director of men's
OL,8,Fhealth research Dr Zac Seidler, the
OL,9,Fduke said there were "conversations
OL,10,Fthat are now happening in households
OL,11,Fbetween kids and parents that never
OL,12,Fexisted between me and my parents".
OL,14,FHe spoke about the evolving roles of
OL,15,Fparents, telling the guests: "From my
OL,16,Fperspective, our kids are our upgrade.
OL,18,F"That's not how I was taught but that
OL,19,Fwas my take on it ` not to say I was
OL,20,Fan upgrade of my dad or that my kids
OL,21,Fare an upgrade of me.
OL,26,@qD@VOUtD@bO]wD@^OUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776243304
OL,3,CHarry: I needed to deal with 'stuff
OL,4,Cfrom the past' before having children
OL,6,F"That's the approach that I take, to
OL,7,Fknow that with the world the way that
OL,8,Fit goes, the kids that we bring up in
OL,9,Ftoday's world need to be an upgrade."
OL,11,FThe duke said there could be a
OL,12,F"disconnection" in the early days of
OL,13,Ffatherhood, adding "certainly I felt a
OL,14,Fdisconnection because my wife was the
OL,15,Fone creating life, and I was there to
OL,16,Fwitness it".
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@eO]tD@AOUtD@OO]uD@TOUxD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776243304
OL,3,CHarry: I needed to deal with 'stuff
OL,4,Cfrom the past' before having children
OL,6,FWearing a taupe shirt and jeans, Harry
OL,7,Fsaid: "I think for many guys, you try
OL,8,Fto think about what service can I
OL,9,Fprovide at this point, because my work
OL,10,Fhere is done to some extent.
OL,12,F"And then when it comes back around
OL,13,Fagain, I think the biggest tip that I
OL,14,Fwas given, actually, from my therapist
OL,15,Fin the UK, was just be aware of how
OL,16,Fyou feel once the baby is born."
OL,18,F"Every single time I went to work and
OL,19,FI came back ` if I was stressed, the
OL,20,Fmoment that I held Archie, he would
OL,21,Fstart crying."
OL,26,@oD@GOUtD@AOUxD@`O]zD@AOU}D@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776243304
OL,3,CHarry: I needed to deal with 'stuff
OL,4,Cfrom the past' before having children
OL,6,FHe added: "Fatherhood is the most
OL,7,Fimportant and sort of transformational
OL,8,Frole that a guy can ever, can ever
OL,9,Fmove into."
OL,11,FHarry also told the audience of
OL,12,FMovember supporters and their children
OL,13,Fthat "I'm fortunate enough to be able
OL,14,Fto work from home".
OL,16,FGiving a talk at a function room of
OL,17,Fthe stadium, he said: "During Covid,
OL,18,Fit was like, well, this working from
OL,19,Fhome thing is really not great when
OL,20,Fyou have like small kids running
OL,21,Faround, jumping into your meetings."
OL,26,@nD@KOUqD@KO]uD@FOUvD@RO]yD@WOU}D@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
