OL,3,CHarry: I needed to deal with 'stuff
OL,4,Cfrom the past' before having children
OL,6,FHarry then took to the Aussie rules
OL,7,Ffootball pitch and had a kickabout
OL,8,Fwith Western Bulldogs players Tom
OL,9,FLiberatore, Adam Treloar and Matthew
OL,10,FKennedy in his Chelsea boots, while
OL,11,Fdiscussing the differences between the
OL,12,Fsport and rugby.
OL,14,FThe duke looked delighted and beamed
OL,15,Fas he ran across the pitch to have a
OL,16,Fkickabout with children, telling one
OL,17,Fboy: "Good kick man" and "it's a
OL,18,Fslippery ball that".
OL,20,FHe also posed for photographs while
OL,21,Fholding a Western Bulldogs scarf.
OL,26,@yD@FOUyD@TO]yD@ZOUzD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
