OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776243304
OL,3,CHarry: I needed to deal with 'stuff
OL,4,Cfrom the past' before having children
OL,6,FHarry also witnessed John Pearce (John
OL,7,FWiggle) and Lachlan Gillespie (Lachy
OL,8,FWiggle) from Australian children's
OL,9,Fmusic group The Wiggles perform on the
OL,10,Fpitch and gave a little wiggle of his
OL,11,Fown in response.
OL,13,FThe Movember movement, founded in
OL,14,FMelbourne in 2003, is a global charity
OL,15,Ffocused on improving men's health,
OL,16,Fparticularly in relation to mental
OL,17,Fhealth, suicide prevention, prostate
OL,18,Fcancer and testicular cancer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
