OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776243304
OL,3,CHarry: I needed to deal with 'stuff
OL,4,Cfrom the past' before having children
OL,6,FThe campaign, which involves men
OL,7,Fgrowing moustaches during the month of
OL,8,FNovember to raise awareness, has
OL,9,Fraised hundreds of millions of pounds
OL,10,Facross more than 20 countries ` with
OL,11,F"Mo" commonly used in Australia as
OL,12,Fslang for moustache.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@DO]
